H0.text: 4 calories of energy is the amount provided by one gram of protein.

H1.text: Two calories of energy are provided by one gram of protein.

H2.text: 1 calorie is the energy provided by one gram of protein.

H3.text: 5 calories of energy are provided by one gram of protein.

A4.text: As fuel, proteins have the same energy density as carbohydrates: 17 kJ (4 kcal) per gram.
